# Implementation Plan: CockroachDB ClusterTopology Component

Build a dark cyberpunk styled React component (`ClusterTopology.tsx`) using Framer Motion for SVG animations and Tailwind CSS to visualize a 3-node CockroachDB cluster with dynamic states (`HEALTHY`, `INCIDENT`, `RECOVERING`).

## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> The component will use an interactive SVG canvas powered by Framer Motion for smooth node pulsing, inter-node packet flow, glowing connecting lines, and animated packet delivery into Node 2 during state recovery.

